I think there is merit in having consistency between how data in rendered in SQL Lab and slices, i.e., there are inconsistencies [here](https://github.com/apache/incubator-superset/issues/3603#issuecomment-373280675) where SQL Lab reports `null` and slices report ` NULL` (with a leading whitespace which messes with alignment).
